column5: Hello Friends! Whoops, forget the test part. Just wondered if anyone could tell me the landscape appearance between Deception and the zig-zag after the fire a couple years back. We are going up there for the opener and wondered how much things had changed. Thanks, RM.
Between the logging and the fire, it's not too good. The fire ended at loon rapids to the east and to the west ended at about the rags
